#

Deruny (Potato Pancakes)

35 min
$10
220 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenEggs

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Ukrainian

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

Comfort FoodEasyHearty

Description

Crispy on the outside, soft and fluffy on the inside, these potato pancakes are a delightful treat!

Ingredients

  • potatoes: 4 medium
  • onion: 1 small
  • eggs: 2 large
  • all-purpose flour: 1/2 cup
  • salt: 1 tsp
  • black pepper: 1/2 tsp
  • vegetable oil: for frying
